Dialogue: 0,00:05:28.760,00:05:46.860,辉英,,0,0,0,,So ui minus 1 is equal to ui minus partial u partial x times delta x plus half of delta x squared partial squared u partial x squared.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:47.180,00:05:48.020,辉英,,0,0,0,,Right.
