Dialogue: 0,00:06:04.640,00:06:07.300,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this term is going to be here.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:08.600,00:06:13.640,辉英,,0,0,0,,And we also have this term, which we have delta x squared divided by delta x.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:14.060,00:06:17.140,辉英,,0,0,0,,So we have a term that is proportional to the second order derivative.
