Dialogue: 0,00:06:31.880,00:06:40.880,辉英,,0,0,0,,amount of numerical dissipation is half of delta x times the characteristic speed. So
Dialogue: 0,00:06:40.880,00:06:47.600,辉英,,0,0,0,,here I would also have half of that times the characteristic speed. So the question
Dialogue: 0,00:06:47.600,00:06:54.040,辉英,,0,0,0,,is why don't we apply upwinding to the linear combinations of variables that has just a
