Dialogue: 0,00:07:01.760,00:07:09.140,辉英,,0,0,0,,changes in time. So for example, if we have a shock wave, then at the next time step,
Dialogue: 0,00:07:09.140,00:07:10.600,辉英,,0,0,0,,even at the same grid point,
Dialogue: 0,00:07:10.600,00:07:10.700,辉英,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,00:07:10.700,00:07:10.860,辉英,,0,0,0,,shock
Dialogue: 0,00:07:10.860,00:07:16.900,辉英,,0,0,0,,wave may have sweeped over the grid point. And therefore, before the time step and after
