Dialogue: 0,00:10:20.020,00:10:25.960,辉英,,0,0,0,,this maximum DFTU would be the absolute value of u plus square root of gh.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:26.800,00:10:32.280,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this term, times u plus 1 minus ui,
Dialogue: 0,00:10:32.280,00:10:34.200,辉英,,0,0,0,,is going to be added.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:36.740,00:10:42.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this is the dissipation flux that you want to add
